title: UVA
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Bakery, Colombian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegetarian food and fish. Has juices, baked goods, salads, sandwiches, and local food. Its bakery offers sugar free, gluten-soy-nut free items. Drinks are prepared with alkaline water. Has Wi-Fi and music playing in the background.
